    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true 'time capsule' find, preserved in showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish, free of rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, thanks to climate-controlled garage storage. Inside, the cabin remains immaculate; the premium leather seats still carry their original scent and show no signs of bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic component and switch functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by authorized technicians. From the pristine alloy wheels to the untouched tool kit in the trunk, this car represents the pinnacle of its model. It is a rare opportunity for an enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
