      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the zenith of automotive preservation. Every facet of this specimen\u2014from its lustrous, factory-original finish to the pristine, untouched interior appointments\u2014reflects a standard of maintenance that transcends the typical market offering. Mechanically flawless and aesthetically peerless, this vehicle has been curated for the most discerning collector who demands uncompromising excellence. We invite you to experience a motorcar that remains indistinguishable from its original delivery state.",
